          "component_id": "customize",
          "data": {
            "data": {
              "parsed_content": [
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "玩法教學",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 2,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "玩法教學1",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "alignment": "center",
                      "type": "custom_image",
                      "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/08/16/125391187/57df4b1a1250c7ef855496edd3382c43_9081237747484936617.png"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "旅行者需要裝備「留影機」，與留影點互動後進入留影模式。留影分為留影設定調整階段，和可以移動以及施放技能的留影階段。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "玩法教學2",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "alignment": "center",
                      "type": "custom_image",
                      "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/08/16/125391187/20170a14809f5514d3edac35a35deaee_295159628689041956.png"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "在留影點調整階段，旅行者首先需要選擇一個留影設定，並可以在此設定的基礎上繼續調整留影的位置和角度。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "需要注意的是，",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:rgb(255, 225, 75)"
                      ],
                      "text": "留影點",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "需要在留影範圍內。確認留影設定後，進入留影階段。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "玩法教學3",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "alignment": "center",
                      "type": "custom_image",
                      "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/08/16/125391187/2837e78705ce084aae0c55ed1046ccfc_2407733174847835579.png"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "在留影階段，當旅行者使用「留影機」拍攝畫片時，畫片完成時的角度將由之前所調整的留影設定決定。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "在留影過程中，留影的方向會由「留影射光」指示。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "玩法教學4",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "alignment": "center",
                      "type": "custom_image",
                      "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/08/16/125391187/d81abd172edd9b8c69e12e7bef909cd3_1865695868843647055.png"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "若想重新調整留影設定，也可以點擊終端挑戰，選擇回到預設重新調整留影設定。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "完成留影後，若想繼續使用目前的留影設定繼續留影，可以點擊繼續留影回到留影階段。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "玩法教學5",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "alignment": "center",
                      "type": "custom_image",
                      "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/10/31/125391187/5d7775f835de3f914717de62227fb320_8388926527176302389.png"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "當實現拍攝目標時即可獲得獎勵。如果同時實現所有目標，活動螢幕上會出現一個額外的標記。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            }
          }
        }
      ]
    }
